# WECLE LP - Cursor Rules

## Project
- WECLE 四條畷店 LP (Landing Page)
- Static HTML/CSS/JS, no frameworks

## Code Style
- Use semantic HTML5 elements (section, nav, header, footer, main, article)
- CSS: BEM-like naming (.section__element--modifier)
- CSS: Mobile-first media queries (min-width)
- CSS: Custom properties for all design tokens
- JS: Vanilla ES6+, no jQuery
- JS: Use addEventListener, not onclick attributes
- All user-facing text in Japanese
- Code comments in English

## Design Tokens (CSS Variables)
```css
--color-primary: #00A5A8;
--color-text: #1A2B3C;
--color-bg: #F5F3F0;
--color-accent: #FF6B35;
--color-gold: #D4A843;
--color-white: #FFFFFF;
--font-family: 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
```

## Responsive Breakpoints
- Base: 375px (mobile-first)
- Tablet: min-width: 768px
- Desktop: min-width: 1024px
- Wide: min-width: 1440px

## Performance Rules
- No render-blocking JS (defer attribute)
- Optimize CSS (no unused selectors)
- Use loading="lazy" for images below fold
- Minimize DOM depth

## Accessibility Rules
- All images must have alt text
- Interactive elements need focus styles
- ARIA attributes on accordion, modal, navigation
- Color contrast 4.5:1 minimum
- Keyboard-navigable FAQ accordion

## GTM/Analytics
- Use dataLayer.push for events
- Event categories: cta_click, faq_open, scroll_depth, phone_tap
- Do NOT include actual GTM container ID (use placeholder GTM-XXXXXX)

## File Scope
- index.html: Structure only, no inline styles/scripts
- css/style.css: All styles
- js/main.js: All interactions
- Do not create new files without approval
